data.title: More Than A Feline
data.meta_description:
More Than A Feline by Cat Temper, released 12 November 2020

1. Sweet Cheetah (feat. Oceanside85)
2. Cat's Eye (feat. Swayze)
3. Claws Out (feat. Jennifer Maher Coleman)
4. Nine Lives (feat. Frisky Monkey)
5. Purrfect Crime (feat. Casey Desmond)
6. Slaves to the Feline Race (feat. Gulf Blvd)
7. Doom Puma (feat. C Z A R I N A)
8. Big Bad Cat (feat. Upon Eventual Collapse)
9. Space Catets (feat. Violet Candide)
10. The Swarm of Ulthar (feat. The Vessel of VVOV)

Cat Temper's first non-instrumental release features the vocal talents of 10 guest singers. They represent a range of styles from sparkly synthpop to growling grindcore. Each vocalist wrote and performed lyrics embodying a unique feline perspective.

Digital download includes a PDF with song lyrics and guest bios.
